==English==
===Noun===
'''bot herd''', also '''bot-herd'''
# {{internet}} A large collection of [[compromised]] systems exploited for malicious purposes.

===Quotations===
'''2005:''' So-called bot herds - networks of compromised PCs under the control of a malicious hacker - continue to be used as launch pads for other types of attack. &mdash; ''[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/technology/4259554.stm  Hackers target net call systems]'' BBC Online, 19 September 2005